      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "摆驾。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00002",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四太监同上，唐王上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00003",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "金乌东升玉兔坠，景阳钟三响把皇催。忆昔当年遭颠沛，国乱只为杨贵妃。安禄山在河东曾起反意，兵困长安夺社稷。杨玉环被困在马嵬驿，可惜她一命受凌逼。先皇逃在西蜀地，多亏了皇兄郭子仪。血战三载狼烟息，才把逆贼剑下劈。到如今乐享太平世，河清海宴凤来仪。内侍臣摆驾九龙椅，孤王有道福寿齐。",
      "text_length": 138
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00004",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "皇后上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00005",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "内侍摆驾金殿里，见了万岁辩是非。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00006",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "妾妃见驾，吾皇万岁。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00007",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "御妻平身。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00008",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "万万岁。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00009",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "赐坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00010",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "谢坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00011",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "御妻上殿，有何本奏？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00012",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "郭暧怒打金枝，万岁做主！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00013",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "孤王不信。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00014",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "万岁宣皇儿上殿一看便知明白。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00015",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "内侍，宣公主上殿。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00016",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00017",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二宫女、公主同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00018",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "呵吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00019",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "忽听见皇传旨意，急忙上殿奏端的。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00020",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00021",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "一见皇儿泪悲啼，打碎珠冠拆破衣。你与驸马因何起？一一从头奏皇知。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00022",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "容禀，",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00023",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "尊父皇容儿本奏起，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00024",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "皇儿平身，赐坐。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00025",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "谢座。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00026",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "细听儿臣奏端的：当朝的驸马太无礼，酒醉回宫把儿欺。他言道父皇的江山从何起？尽多是他们父子功劳争来的。孩儿未曾回半句，他那里拳打足又踢。不是婆婆进宫里，孩儿险些命归西。有一句话儿不好启：脱去了旧衣换新衣。父王快快传旨意，不斩驸马儿不依。",
      "text_length": 117
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00027",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "君比天来臣比地，天翻地覆世间稀。郭暧打了吾皇女，打皇儿犹如把万岁欺。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00028",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "御妻休要把本奏起，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00029",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "啊吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00030",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "皇儿也莫泪悲啼。郭暧不是皇降罪，",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00031",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "谢父王！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00032",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "且慢，",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00033",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "联恐其中儿有非。你母女暂且回宫去，",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00034",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "我这里带皇儿转回宫里。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00035",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "皇后"
      ],
      "text": "走吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00036",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "公主"
      ],
      "text": "啊吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00037",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "皇后、公主同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00038",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "内侍与孤传旨意，快宣汾阳郭子仪。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00039",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "郭子仪上殿！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00040",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "领旨！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00041",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "汾阳王绑蠢子珠泪撇地，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00042",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭暧上，郭子仪上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00043",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "奴才！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00044",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "大骂奴才听端的：安禄山在河东曾起反意，将我主驾逼在琴西。那时为父不得地，多亏了太白先生把本提。他将为父荐朝里，挂帅才把逆贼劈。儿酒后打了皇王女，连累我白发苍苍受凌逼。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00045",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹休要怒不息，孩儿言来听端的：他既皇王玉叶体，不该与臣配夫妻；既与臣子来婚配，为论什么高来论什么低？儿今打了皇王女，论皇法不过是剥儿的皮！",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00046",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "小奴才说话大有理，问得老夫无话提。父子们同到金銮殿，",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00047",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "跪下！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00048",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "儿要端端正正跪，且待为父把本提。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00049",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "九龙口内红光起，来了皇兄郭子仪。昨日皇兄寿诞日，孤未曾去拜寿，未曾赐给你的酒席。孤坐江山全仗你，从今后见孤免屈膝。内侍臣与孤忙搀起，君臣们对坐把话提。",
      "text_length": 75
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00050",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "绑坏了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00051",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "殿角下绑的何臣子？一一从头奏皇知。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00052",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "绑的郭暧不成器，酒后无端把君欺。请皇传旨将他斩，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00053",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "且慢，",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00054",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "老皇兄做事太心急。况且驸马幼年纪，公主又是少年妻，自古道清官难断家务事，他夫妻们吵闹是常有的。孤皇传旨不降罪，",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00055",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "松绑。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00056",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "驸马到后宫换朝衣。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00057",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭暧下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00058",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "万岁不降郭暧罪，背地喜煞郭子仪。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00059",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "郭子仪见驾，吾皇万岁！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00060",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "平身，赐坐。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00061",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "谢坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00062",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "皇兄，驸马与公主吵闹，皇兄怎么知晓？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00063",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "老臣正在银安标本，忽听内侍来报，才得知晓。万岁宣小奴才上殿，一问便知明白。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00064",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "内侍，宣驸马冠带上殿。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00065",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "驸马冠带上殿！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00066",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "领旨！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00067",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭暧上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00068",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "适才如遇阴曹地，鬼门关前七魄归。臣郭暧见驾，吾皇万岁！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00069",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "驸马平身。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00070",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "万万岁！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00071",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "驸马为了何事，与公主吵闹？当殿奏来。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00072",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "容奏：臣逢尧舜之主，蒙恩将公主匹配。自盘古以来，只有妻拜夫，那有反礼而行？",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00073",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "唔，听奴才之言，把我君臣大礼，一旦抛废！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00074",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "这个……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00075",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "皇兄，此乃是公主故作威福。从今以后，将红灯撇去，也不用三四诏，驸马有何本章当殿奏来。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00076",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "容奏：昨日臣父母八旬双寿，满朝文武，众家各嫂，一个个成双作对，拜寿堂前。公主不去拜寿，到也罢了。连问安二字，全然无有。大非儿媳之道。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00077",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "哈！想公主乃金枝玉叶，岂向我臣门拜寿？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00078",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "想东宫太子，他是守缺之龙，怎么过府拜寿?",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00079",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "想小千岁，他乃奉了万岁的旨意。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00080",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "公主不去拜寿，也是奉了他父的旨意么？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00081",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "这个……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00082",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "皇兄，听驸马所奏，孤皇心下明白了：昨日你二老八旬双寿，满朝文武，众家各嫂，一个个成双作对，拜寿堂前。驸马有妻，不能孝敬父母。自觉孝道有亏，是与不是？",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00083",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "诚如圣谕。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00084",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "吓，皇兄，古人有言，道是“不痴不聋，不作家翁”。从今以后，他夫妻闺房之事，你要少管。听孤旨下：",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00085",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "驸马奏本孤的龙心爽，深知三纲并五常。臣心若得君欢畅，福寿齐眉永安康。老皇兄暂且回府上，孤与驸马有商量。",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00086",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "辞别万岁下殿往，背转身来自揣详。皇恩浩荡真浩荡，天降明主掌大唐。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00087",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭子仪下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00088",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "驸马近前听旨降：",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00089",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "忠臣孝子永留芳。曾记得安贼来反上，你父子领兵去到边疆。孤皇赐你大红蟒，忠孝碑匾挂高堂。再赐一口上方剑，巡查内外与宫墙。倘若是公主近心强，你只管把本一本一本奏孤皇。驸马暂且回府往，公主赔罪到汾阳。",
      "text_length": 97
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00090",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭暧"
      ],
      "text": "辞别万岁下殿往，公主赔罪到汾阳。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00091",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭暧下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00092",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "唐王"
      ],
      "text": "驸马犯罪难发放，难道说为皇儿斩杀忠良？死罪不降反而加赏，买动他父子们忠心好助孤皇。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01002007_e00093",
      "play_id": "01002007",
      "scene_id": "01002007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "同下。",
      "text_length": 3
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}